{"tid":1069830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲最強奶媽挺F乳跳繩　《蘋果》宅視角重現","createTime":"2019-03-20T08:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T09:02:56.000Z","uid":1121,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7cce3863dba42f2bd7c73654d63bb3c027a95e98","tid":1069830,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"24歲雪乳辣媽網紅直播主Vivian，上個月在臉書社團「爆廢公社」分享踏步機運動畫面，引發網友暴動。她應允網友要求，17日再分享一段7秒鐘的跳繩影片，傲人上圍波濤洶湧，吸引超過36萬次點閱，再度震暈粉絲，Vivian昨天應《蘋果》邀訪，穿上影片內的性感裝扮晃乳跳繩，經典重現。<br />\n<br />\n「誤打誤撞，想說可以在家賺錢，順便照顧小孩子。」Vivian已婚，與大12歲的美髮造型師育有一子，常在粉絲團分享生活、曬小孩，直播主事業做得火紅，被網友封為「最強奶媽」。Vivian說，跟網友的話題很隨興，通常依時事而定，看大家喜歡聊什麼都可以聊，像前陣子立委補選就聊政治，或者聊運動與畫畫，最近就聊IG、fb當機的影響，「我當時畫了《聖鬥士星矢》，卻怎麼都貼不上去，還以為被屏蔽，還滿崩潰的！」後來才知道系統大當機，一整晚寢食難安、徹夜難眠。<br />\n因父母工作地關係，Vivian兩度長住加拿大共計13年，擁有F奶傲人雪乳，Vivian說：「這樣的身材在加拿大那邊都差不多，因此不會特別注意，但在台灣就顯得比較豐滿。」除了遺傳媽媽的好身材，Vivian飲食方面喜歡吃控肉飯、義大利麵、牛肉麵、乳製品、速食，下廚會煮麻婆豆腐、咖哩飯，喜歡游泳。Vivian考取多倫多大學美術系與獸醫系，選擇在美術系註冊就讀，但為了維繫在台男友的遠距離愛情，也想陪陪照顧她長大的奶奶、盡盡孝道，決定返台。<br />\n擁有傲人的F奶，Vivian的困擾是「買衣服不好買！」她說，胸圍大，穿起來容易顯胖，內衣不好選，後來有女網友推薦比較好的款式，才慢慢解決這個問題。Vivian喜歡自己又直又白的美腿，睡前會抬腳、按摩，至於美胸並沒有特別保養，平常就是多運動，擦乳液。<br />\n「張貼性感美照，一開始只是想分享生活日常。」Vivian沒想到引發網友暴動，網友加碼跪求「跳繩影片」，她也從善如流，穿上短T、熱褲與紅色外套，在學校操場錄一段「7秒」的跳繩影片，畫面一貼出，粉絲再度被乳浪震暈，紛紛留言「這個影片為什麼不會停，浪費我20分鐘」、「好無聊，我看了7749遍手機差點沒ㄉㄧㄢˋ」、「好晃@@頭暈流鼻血了」、「我是匈奴族長」、「跳繩果然是好東西」。影片效果佳，Vivian表示會再精進影片內容與穿搭。<br />\n網友瘋傳「雙手捧右奶」美照，Vivian說，當時因餵母乳，罩杯三級跳至I罩杯，她特別拍下來留念分享。對於網路直播工作，家人與先生都很尊重，「只要不傷風敗俗，做好自己本分就好，網友的評論甚至騷擾，都不會特別放在心上。」Vivian說，目前直播工作暫時「半隱退」，希望朝多元平台發展，看能否出演宮廷劇，或參加憲哥的節目「綜藝玩很大」玩遊戲，與民眾同樂。<br />\nVivian表示，人都是視覺動物，一開始可能會被外型吸引，「但我也扮過如花、無臉男呀！我喜歡帶給大家歡樂、讓身邊的人開懷大笑，多看看我，多了解我，其實會發現我是很有趣的人。」網紅直播大受歡迎，Vivian得等小孩睡著之後，從午夜12點開始直播，直到清晨六、七點小孩起床，只能睡兩三小時，賺到一點尿布奶粉錢，後來健康出了問題，Vivian認為時間應該花在家人身上，對於這份光環與收入不再戀棧，3個多月前決定退出直播工作。<br />\n「我選擇在這個最光榮的時間點退出直播平台，希望大家永遠都會記得，有一個開心果帶給大家歡樂，這份美好的畫面與回憶就保留給大家。」Vivian溫情向粉絲告別，但她希望網友還是可以持續追蹤IG，保持互動。（林建鋒／台中報導）<br />\n█ Vivian小檔案<br />\n姓名：謝薇安<br />\n年齡：24歲<br />\n身高：165公分<br />\n體重：52公斤<br />\n星座：天秤<br />\n血型：O型<br />\n學歷：多倫多大學美術系(肄)          <br />\n三圍：36F/25/32<br />\n家庭狀況：已婚、育有一子(3歲)<br />\n臉書粉絲團追蹤人數：19.2萬  <br />\nIG追蹤人數：78萬<br />\n興趣：畫畫、追劇、美甲<br />\n最喜歡自己哪個部位：腿 <br />\n直播主資歷：2年半<br />\n月收：曾破六位數，其餘保密"},{"pid":"741d2a1c4be493e65d04529a4164fad57ec0428b","tid":1069830,"uid":1121,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_a61b5413ca83df45c64b0fc74b03a5b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_a61b5413ca83df45c64b0fc74b03a5b1.jpg&h=79783416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVivian為《蘋果》讀者重現跳繩畫面，但光是暖身就已經讓人噴鼻血。林建鋒攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_1b2350d5edddc562068eaa1aa5cfb818.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_1b2350d5edddc562068eaa1aa5cfb818.jpg&h=931cd270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVivian為《蘋果》讀者重現跳繩畫面。林建鋒攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_551798af58d6f62cee6ed29ab7a33ed2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_551798af58d6f62cee6ed29ab7a33ed2.jpg&h=cace9f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF奶辣媽Vivian示範跳繩，運動神經還不錯。林建鋒攝"},{"pid":"2fba99f372f99ed767c7063d8f7ead8afed52370","tid":1069830,"uid":102475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"Hello moto"},{"pid":"cb07537e3c582133a94ca42906082cf3c218be96","tid":1069830,"uid":68803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"片呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4ecaa9cbad747acc36ca4242305c5f741964dc","tid":1069830,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"最盡500"},{"pid":"623bbcb38bf60280485dd7727b50a04ff973a3cc","tid":1069830,"uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_60362c7f21d2498db5fbc706c95be748.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_60362c7f21d2498db5fbc706c95be748.jpg&h=36fb7e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVivian脫下紅色外套，用另一種造型跳看看。林建鋒攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_5649cf1643c10e4bd6db401abd470b2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_5649cf1643c10e4bd6db401abd470b2d.jpg&h=d309e693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVivian以緊身短T再度上陣，只見波濤洶湧浪潮起伏。林建鋒攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_e154538e02d5a082198da2bae95fa668.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_e154538e02d5a082198da2bae95fa668.jpg&h=a49726dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVivian表示哺乳時漲到I罩杯(左、Vivian提供)，受訪時再示範當時雙手捧右乳的畫面。林建鋒攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_f1c367a361c057d04d6c2b8553649a43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_f1c367a361c057d04d6c2b8553649a43.jpg&h=15d589ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橫看成嶺側成峰，記者突然想吟詩。林建鋒攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_be8a0492553095be88ce29d77de09f2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_be8a0492553095be88ce29d77de09f2b.jpg&h=2b49c0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVivian不吝展示好身材。Vivian提供<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190320/640_4d53fab8d19cf835d82a2a0f5cc40df9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190320%2F640_4d53fab8d19cf835d82a2a0f5cc40df9.jpg&h=597a4989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVivian已婚，育有三歲兒子。Vivian提供"},{"pid":"f5677b861d47077b3dee16cc701799fd6919fca8","tid":1069830,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:20:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190320/1536275/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0WTvP1kWv1wbKSex1WdhQmEgs25vZASgXOzUOrVbpFQli67NoZYiPmiY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190320%2F1536275%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0WTvP1kWv1wbKSex1WdhQmEgs25vZASgXOzUOrVbpFQli67NoZYiPmiY8&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9OBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=f2a59596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190320%2F1536275%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0WTvP1kWv1wbKSex1WdhQmEgs25vZASgXOzUOrVbpFQli67NoZYiPmiY8&h=11df3c28\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190320/1536275/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0WTvP1kWv1wbKSex1WdhQmEgs25vZASgXOzUOrVbpFQli67NoZYiPmiY8</a>"},{"pid":"23d9705d11dffd268a9791ffcb68fa372a5556de","tid":1069830,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"臺女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7e7964418b4fc6d53e5838f4808ad4dfd5b363","tid":1069830,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal